 Notes |\\n    14→|---|---|---|---|\\n    15→| `sessionStart` | `session-start` | `SessionStart` | Session begins or resumes |\\n    16→| `sessionEnd` | `session-end` | `SessionEnd` | Session completes/terminated |\\n    17→| `userPromptSubmitted` | `user-prompt-submitted` | `TurnStart` | User submits prompt |\\n    18→| `agentStop` | `agent-stop` | `TurnEnd` | Agent finished responding |\\n    19→| `subagentStop` | `subagent-stop` | `SubagentEnd` | Subagent completed |\\n    20→| `preToolUse` | `pre-tool-use` | `nil` | Pass-through |\\n    21→| `postToolUse` | `post-tool-use` | `nil` | Pass-through |\\n    22→| `errorOccurred` | `error-occurred` | `nil` | Logging only |\\n    23→\\n    24→**Common stdin fields** (all hooks): `timestamp`, `cwd`, `sessionId`, `hookEventName`, `transcript_path`\\n    25→\\n    26→**Hook-specific fields**: `source`/`initialPrompt` (sessionStart), `reason` (sessionEnd), `prompt` (userPromptSubmitted), `toolName`/`toolArgs` (preToolUse/postToolUse), `toolResult` (postToolUse), `error` (errorOccurred)\\n    27→\\n    28→---\\n    29→\\n    30→## Step 0: Verify Hook stdin Format\\n    31→\\n    32→**Before writing code**, capture actual stdin JSON to confirm the common fields and `agentStop`/`subagentStop` format:\\n    33→\\n    34→```json\\n    35→{\\n    36→  \\\"version\\\": 1,\\n    37→  \\\"hooks\\\": {\\n    38→    \\\"sessionStart\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"bash\\\": \\\"cat > /tmp/copilot-session-start.json\\\", \\\"timeoutSec\\\": 10}],\\n    39→    \\\"agentStop\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"bash\\\": \\\"cat > /tmp/copilot-agent-stop.json\\\", \\\"timeoutSec\\\": 10}],\\n    40→    \\\"userPromptSubmitted\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"command\\\", \\\"bash\\\": \\\"cat > /tmp/copilot-user-prompt.json\\\", \\\"timeoutSec\\\": 10}]\\n    41→  }\\n    42→}\\n    43→```\\n    44→\\n    45→Place at `.github/hooks/copilot-setup.json`, run `copilot`, check `/tmp/copilot-*.json`. Confirm `sessionId` and `transcript_path` are present.\\n    46→\\n    47→---\\n    48→\\n    49→## Step 1: Add Registry Constants\\n    50→\\n    51→**File**: `cmd/entire/cli/agent/registry.go`\\n    52→\\n    53→```go\\n    54→// In AgentName constants:\\n    55→AgentNameCopilot AgentName = \\\"github-copilot\\\"\\n    56→\\n    57→// In AgentType constants:\\n    58→AgentTypeCopilot AgentType = \\\"GitHub Copilot\\\"\\n    59→```\\n    60→\\n    61→---\\n    62→\\n    63→## Step 2: Create `cmd/entire/cli/agent/copilot/types.go`\\n    64→\\n    65→Follow `geminicli/types.go` pattern. Copilot uses camelCase JSON fields.\\n    66→\\n    67→**Hook config types:**\\n    68→```go\\n    69→type CopilotHookConfig struct {\\n    70→    Version int                           `json:\\\"version\\\"`\\n    71→    Hooks   map[string][]CopilotHookEntry `json:\\\"hooks\\\"`\\n    72→}\\n    73→\\n    74→type CopilotHookEntry struct {\\n    75→    Type       string `json:\\\"type\\\"`\\n    76→    Bash       string `json:\\\"bash\\\"`\\n    77→    TimeoutSec int    `json:\\\"timeoutSec,omitempty\\\"`\\n    78→}\\n    79→```\\n    80→\\n    81→**Common stdin base (embedded in all hook input structs):**\\n    82→```go\\n    83→type hookBase struct {\\n    84→    SessionID      string `json:\\\"sessionId\\\"`\\n    85→    TranscriptPath string `json:\\\"transcript_path\\\"`\\n    86→    Cwd            string `json:\\\"cwd\\\"`\\n    87→    HookEventName  string `json:\\\"hookEventName\\\"`\\n    88→    Timestamp      string `json:\\\"timestamp\\\"`\\n    89→}\\n    90→```\\n    91→\\n    92→**Hook-specific stdin types:**\\n    93→- `sessionStartRaw` - embeds `hookBase` + `Source string`, `InitialPrompt string`\\n    94→- `sessionEndRaw` - embeds `hookBase` + `Reason string`\\n    95→- `userPromptRaw` - embeds `hookBase` + `Prompt string`\\n    96→- `agentStopRaw` - embeds `hookBase` (no extra fields expected)\\n    97→- `subagentStopRaw` - embeds `hookBase` (+ possibly subagent metadata)\\n    98→- `toolUseRaw` - emb